## EMAIL TONE
The email is sent to the application team who may not be technical.
  ✓ Professional and clear
  ✓ Action-oriented — what do they need to do?
  ✓ Factual — only confirmed data
  ✗ No alarm language — no "CRITICAL", "EMERGENCY", "URGENT WARNING"
  ✗ No technical jargon — no WinRM, boot time timestamps in raw format,
    no validation agent references
  ✗ No apologies or filler — straight to the point